obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line 4
  line `CHAPTER V`
  line `G RANT, SUSPENSION OR CANCELLATION OF PERMIT`
  line `S ECTIONS.`
  line `27. Application for permit.`
  line `28. Liability of owner or Operator in certain cases.`
  line `29. Suspension or cancellation of permit.`
  line `CHAPTER VI`
  line `I NSPECTIONS`
  line `30. Inspection in India.`
  line `31. Inspection of international facilities.`
  line `32. Obstruction and false information.`
  line `CHAPTER VII`
  line `W ASTE DISPOSAL AND WASTE MANAGEMENT`
  line `33. Waste disposal.`
  line `34. Establishment of waste classification system and waste management plans.`
  line `35. Removal of waste from Antarctica.`
  line `36. Disposal of combustive wastes.`
  line `37. Storage of wastes.`
  line `CHAPTER VIII`
  line `P REVENTION OF MARINE POLLUTION AND LIABILITY FOR ENVIRONMENTAL`
  line EMERGENCY
  line `38. Committee to ensure compliance of international obligations.`
  line `39. Duties and liabilities of Operator in case of environmental emergency.`
  line `40. Exemption of Operator from liability in certain cases.`
  line `CHAPTER IX`
  line `O FFENCES AND PENALTIES`
  line `41. Penalty for contravention of certain provisions of Act by person.`
  line `42. Penalty for contravention of certain provisions of Act involving vessel.`
  line `43. Penalty for contravention of certain provisions of Act involving aircraft.`
  line `44. Penalty where no provision made in Act.`
  line `45. Offences by companies.`
  line `CHAPTER X`
  line `M ISCELLANEOUS`
  line `46. Constitution of fund.`
